node.text: Haven’t been too consistent with my work outs lately. Still need to remember that I used to pray to be where I am today. Here’s a little progress update. I still train once a week w my trainer but don’t get too the gym as much as I would like. I have been focusing on building my quads and obliques recently. If you have a work out split please comment below what it is. I think a work out split will keep me more motivated.
